title: [LFT] Looking for Bronze/Silver/Gold players for 5v5 team
body:

NOT LOOKING FOR SOMEONE TO JOIN JUST FOR A FEW GAMES. Just a few quick details i'd like to see, Give me an add if i don't get back to anyone or to discuss more.
